Description:Last-known-information regression (CR 608.2h). P2 controls Sedge Troll (2/2 base) and a Swamp, so the Troll is a 3/3 via its continuous static buff. P1 casts Swords to Plowshares on it: the Troll is exiled and P2 gains 3 life — the Troll's power AS IT LAST EXISTED on the battlefield (with the Swamp buff), captured before the exile strips the static. A naive post-exile read would wrongly yield 2.

